# Workflow Orchestration Boundary

Use this when one user action triggers multiple dependent side effects.

- Implement orchestration in `backend/app/features/**/service.py` (or focused workflow modules).
- Keep routers transport-thin (auth, parsing, delegation, HTTP mapping).
- Do not orchestrate domain workflows in frontend components.
- Prefer one intent command endpoint that executes full flow atomically where possible.
- Return updated state/projections so UI can re-sync from server truth.
